      "name": "refine_rpeaks_with_refractory_window",
      "description": "Walk through the candidate indices in order, enforcing a minimum inter-peak spacing of v_300ms; for each accepted candidate, locate the true R-peak as the argmax of the original signal within the following v_100ms samples.",
